INTRODUCTION
	Itsy is a minimalistic view-controller PHP framework.
	For further information please see doc/README

LICENSE
	Itsy is released under the MIT License, please see doc/LICENSE for more
	details.

STATUS
	Itsy should be considered 'alpha' software; any may be subject to major changes.

INSTALLING/USING
	Clone the git repository, configure your http server to use public_html as
	a virtual hosts 'document root', check out the results in your web browser.
	
CREDITS
	Original code and ideas inspired by Mikhail Panchenko's Wheel Framework.
	http://mihasya.com/